<body>
	<div style="position:absolute;left:50%;margin-left:-237px;top:0px;width:612px;height:792px;border-style:outset;overflow:hidden">
		<div style="position:absolute;left:0px;top:0px">
		<img src="{{ asset('assets/images/vission-2020/background1.jpg') }}" width=612 height=792></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:249.17px;top:73.44px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">SXD VISION 2020</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:63.86px;top:106.10px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">St. Xavier’s School has been a Jesuit institution with one history but many stories, one fire</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:63.86px;top:120.98px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">with many sparks; it forms men and women for others, men and women who display</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:63.86px;top:135.86px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">competence, commitment, conscience and compassion.</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:63.86px;top:164.90px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">We firmly believe that St. Xavier’s is the work of God and it shall continue and excel in the</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:63.86px;top:179.66px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">days to come.</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:63.86px;top:208.70px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">We celebrated a GOLDEN JUBILEE of the School in 2010 and continue to celebrate the</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:63.86px;top:223.58px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">legacy of 56 years and pledge to prosper with our motto, </span><span class="cls_004">“UTSAH SIDHDHAYE.”(Strive to</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:63.86px;top:238.10px" class="cls_004"><span class="cls_004">Excel)</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:63.86px;top:267.05px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">We journey with dedication and determination to illuminate the minds of many with</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:63.86px;top:281.93px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">enduring wisdom. It is a march towards new directions of expansion, both academic and</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:63.86px;top:296.69px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">infrastructure. We have initiated </span><span class="cls_005">SXD VISION 2020.</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:63.86px;top:325.61px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">Though it has already made its mark in the world of education, it needs to expand so that it</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:63.86px;top:342.89px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">can cater to a larger number of meritorious as well as needy students in the days to come.</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:63.86px;top:369.77px" class="cls_005"><span class="cls_005">HISTORY OF THE SCHOOL</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:63.86px;top:396.53px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">The School was established in 1960 and it has gone through certain extensions in the course</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:63.86px;top:413.69px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">of time. In 1963, a part of the present building in the Senior Section was completed while in</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:63.86px;top:430.87px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">1974- 76, the present Primary section building came into existence. In 1984, the school</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:63.86px;top:448.03px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">celebrated its Silver Jubilee and as a remembrance it added another section of the building</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:63.86px;top:465.19px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">in the Senior Section. These extensions were quite sufficient till we had only classes from</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:63.86px;top:482.47px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">KG to X.</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:63.86px;top:509.35px" class="cls_005"><span class="cls_005">UPGRADATION OF THE SCHOOL</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:63.86px;top:536.11px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">In 2001, the School upgraded itself to Senior Secondary Level. It has a very good beginning.</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:63.86px;top:553.27px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">We started only with Science Stream of 2 sections and in 2006 we also added Commerce</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:63.86px;top:570.43px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">stream. Thus at Plus Two we have occupied 8 different class rooms. At the moment it is</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:63.86px;top:587.71px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">running very well.</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:63.86px;top:614.74px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">Meanwhile,  the  School  progressed  in  its  performances;  it  could  be  academics  or  co</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:63.86px;top:631.90px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">curricular activities. It regained its name and fame and parents are at a large number start</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:63.86px;top:649.06px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">seeking admissions of their wards in St. Xavier’s School Doranda. Above all, we are very</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:63.86px;top:666.22px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">happy that we are able to admit 40 to 45 percent our tribal and Christian students in the</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:63.86px;top:683.26px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">whole of School. With this need we have increased one more sections from classes Prep to X</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:63.86px;top:700.54px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">which requires 11 additional Class rooms.</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:63.86px;top:727.66px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">It is also to be noted that the whole structure at the moment has been sufficient enough to</span></div>
		</div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:50%;margin-left:-237px;top:802px;width:612px;height:792px;border-style:outset;overflow:hidden">
		<div style="position:absolute;left:0px;top:0px">
		<img src="{{ asset('assets/images/vission-2020/background2.jpg') }}" width=612 height=792></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:63.86px;top:71.40px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">fulfill the needs of initial periods. Now we require better and more infrastructure to meet</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:63.86px;top:88.70px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">the various needs of the students and their parents.</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:63.86px;top:115.82px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">RATIONALE OF SXD VISION 2020</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:81.86px;top:142.82px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">1.  In the Senior Section, we have 5.15 acres of land. It has a big playground which we</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:99.86px;top:159.98px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">like to develop further. However, at the moment we require a separate Plus two</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:99.86px;top:177.14px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">building with better facilities in terms of Library, Computer Lab, Science Labs, Class</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:99.86px;top:194.30px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">rooms, Conference rooms, staff rooms, multipurpose hall etc for which we have SXD</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:99.86px;top:211.46px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">VISION 2020.</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:81.86px;top:228.62px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">2.  The above mentioned facilities will be made available for all the students. However,</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:99.86px;top:245.78px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">they will be more utilized by Senior Secondary Students, which are lacking at the</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:99.86px;top:262.97px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">moment.</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:81.86px;top:280.13px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">3.  Expansion is necessary to cater to a larger number of meritorious as well as needy</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:99.86px;top:297.29px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">students in the days to come.</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:81.86px;top:314.33px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">4.  We have increased one more section in each standard. It means that we need 11 extra</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:99.86px;top:331.49px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">rooms.</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:81.86px;top:348.65px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">5.</span><span class="cls_006"> </span><span class="cls_003"> In 2020, the School will complete its 60</span><span class="cls_007">th</span><span class="cls_003"> Years. We would like to celebrate 2020 with</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:99.86px;top:365.81px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">gratitude with the members of the Society of Jesus, staff, students and their parents</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:99.86px;top:382.97px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">and our esteemed alumni.</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:63.86px;top:427.13px" class="cls_005"><span class="cls_005">NETWORKING & COLLABORATION</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:63.86px;top:453.91px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">Our endeavor to spread our wings towards new horizons requires a consistent cooperation</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:63.86px;top:471.07px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">and collaboration. We have called upon the Members of Doranda Old Xaverians (An</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:63.86px;top:488.23px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">Association of the Alumni), and parents of our students and our well wishers within the</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:63.86px;top:505.39px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">country and outside to come forward to participate in the process of development and</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:63.86px;top:522.55px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">expansion of an institution of learning so that it can serve the nation better in the times to</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:63.86px;top:539.71px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">come. The Doranda Old Xaverians have been able to network with 2600 alumni within and</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:63.86px;top:556.99px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">outside the overseas at the moment with whom they are regularly in contact.</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:63.86px;top:583.99px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">Based on the financial viability and the financial management, we would like to complete</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:63.86px;top:601.27px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">SXD VISION 2020 projects in 2 years. .</span></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;left:258.41px;top:657.46px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">OUR PROJECT</span></div>
		</div>
